---
title: Quick Honey-Garlic Soy Chicken with Buttery Corn and Sticky Rice
description: Crispy, coated chicken pieces are tossed in a sweet and savoury sauce for this wow-worthy dinner. Sticky rice and buttered corn kernels are the perfect accompaniments for a Korean-inspired experience!

